17:47.360 --> 17:48.679
Sorry.

17:59.520 --> 18:01.033
Evenin', Guv'nor.

18:03.520 --> 18:05.670
What's up your bum?

18:05.760 --> 18:08.593
You know why I wanted
that to be you in <i>The Fugitive?</i>

18:08.680 --> 18:12.070
