nothing more than a jerk

18:20.640 --> 18:23.438
who likes to mess with people
for no reason.

18:25.400 --> 18:26.719
Kimble!

18:30.760 --> 18:33.115
You tell anybody, I'll kill you.

18:33.920 --> 18:35.194
Good night, Efram.

18:36.920 --> 18:39.070
Good night, Doctor.

18:40.120 --> 18:42.839
<i>Some people hide</i>
<i>from who they really are.</i>

18:44.200 --> 18:46.430
Baby, Todd and I
are going to the arcade.

18:46.520 --> 18:49.318
I'm going to get some quarters
out your purse.

18:50.840 --> 18:52.114
I'm old.

18:52.200 --> 18:54.589
<i>Others eventually accept who they are.</i>

18:54.680 --> 18:57.592
I'm older. Would you please
get me down to my damn car?

18:59.000 --> 19:01.434
Sure. Let's get
your big Irish ass to your car

19:01.520 --> 19:06.116
so nobody knows you hurt your back.
Let's not worry about my back.

19:08.040 --> 19:09.871
<i>Sometimes it's the tough moments</i>

19:09.960 --> 19:13.396
<i>that help you realise</i>
<i>who you've finally become.</i>

19:14.800 --> 19:17.030
You work in there?

19:17.120 --> 19:18.872
What do you do?

19:18.960 --> 19:21.520
I'm a doctor.
You shouldn't smoke.

